<p style="text-align:start"><strong>Bay Path Skilled Nursing Home &amp; Rehabilitation &bull; </strong>Bay Path Rehabilitation &amp; Nursing Center in Duxbury is a 120-bed skilled center offering short-term rehabilitation and long-term care, nestled among the pines in the beautiful seaside community of Duxbury.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">Bay Path specializes in cases that are medically complex. The center is accredited by&nbsp;<a href="http://www.jointcommission.org/" style="outline: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169); text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">The Joint Commission&nbsp;</a>and is Medicaid/Medicare Certified. The staff is committed to providing high quality medical, nursing and rehabilitative care. Our programs are designed to respect dignity and individuality, allowing every resident to experience the best quality of life while maintaining or regaining function, health and well-being.</p>  <p style="text-align:start">&nbsp;</p>  <ul style="list-style-type:disc; margin-left:40px"> 	<li><a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/senior-living-resources/skilled-nursing-faq" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_self">Click here for Frequently Asked Questions about Skilled Nursing</a></li> 	<li><a href="http://www.welchhrg.com/_pdfs/WelchRehabNursing.brochure2015Update_v4_FINAL.pdf" style="outline: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(17, 113, 169);" target="_blank">Click here for our Rehabilitation Brochure</a><br /> 	&nbsp;</li> </ul>  <p style="text-align:start">In addition to a range of comfortable private and semi-private rooms, Bay Path features a wide range of restaurant-style dining options, including a Sunrise Breakfast, Lunch Club and Supper Club. Socialization is a significant part of the Lunch Club. Bay Path features many common areas including a tavern and tearoom and a bright, sunny courtyard. The center also offers a hair salon, complimentary telephone and cable television, therapeutic recreational activities and ample free parking.</p> 